722362f-a.title: Manhattan: Park Avenue - 86th Street
722362f-a.text:
Park Avenue, east side, from 87th to 86th Streets, showing No. 1049
Park Avenue, an apartment house about four years old. The old
3-story frame No. 1047 together with the small builcings to the
corner of 86th Street, is shortly to be demolished. Compure
picture taken from 86th Street early in 1924.
1922.
John Wallace Gillier, Photographer.
Gift of E. M. Jenks.
